Package sqltoregex.settings.regexgenerator

Interface IRegExGenerator<T>

Type Parameters:
T - String, List of String or SimpleDateFormat
All Known Implementing Classes:
DateAndTimeFormatSynonymGenerator, OrderRotation, RegExGenerator, SpellingMistake, StringSynonymGenerator, SynonymGenerator
public interface IRegExGenerator<T>
The RegExGenerator interface defines methods for use in the respective deparser. The implementation takes place in the respective interface implementations.
